social_posts.post_text: Seasons greetings to you all from malifluous AI microchip Father Christmas! I generated these with the amazing 'Dream Textures' Blender addon. I even generated some cool seamless Christmas wrapping paper too!

It's Christmas eve! But why the salt shaker and sauce bottle?? They were part of a recent project for a new Edinburgh-based production company called Salt 'n' Sauce (the chip shop scene is designed to play in the background of their website)

I just recieved my copy of the Computer Generated book from @gingkopress! In 2021 I was invited to contribute  along with lots of great artists (all their names are on the back!) Thanks to Kyle Goodrich for asking me to be involved. I especially love the textured polygonal front cover

1... 2... aaaaand SPLAAaaSH!!💦 The first of three animations I made for @starface to show off their new Big Blue clamshell case

Art Director: Paige Kozak

Spa day at the car wash!🧼🫧 2nd of 3 animations I made for @starface

Check out BY's theme park ride! Another animation I made recently for @starface with sound design by @pkkozak
One of 22 little characters I created for @uncommon_ldn and @monzo this summer! I think this curry was my favourite
Meet me in the spray booth, it's time to tan!
Plating up another meal! No idea what those prawns would taste like

Thanks for all the suggestions in my stories yesterday ❤️‍🔥 the shop is now open! At the moment its what I have left of my current stock and I'll start on some new designs and restocking over the next while. Thanks to those of you who have already snagged something, I'll get orders out to you next week!
